                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center">Who am I?
                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                    <!--<img class="img-responsive img-circle" src="img/intro-pic.jpg" alt="">-->
                    <hr class="visible-xs">
                    <p>I am a software and web developer living in the Lehigh Valley of Pennsylvania.  I developed an interest in computer science in middle school and have never looked back since.  I love solving puzzles, learning new things, and applying my skills as a programmer to things that I love.  My favorite things to do include producing interesting things with my skillset, relaxing with my girlfriend, and embracing geekdom.</p>
